%F A071797 a(n) = 1 + A053186(n-1).
%F A071797 a(n) = n - 1 - ceiling(sqrt(n))*(ceiling(sqrt(n))-2); n > 0.
%F A071797 a(n) = n - floor(sqrt(n-1))^2, distance between n and the next smaller square. - _Marc LeBrun_, Jan 14 2004
